<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.4594129>
        a                        fabio:Figure ;
        dc:description           "Figure 6. Male postabdomen of Exorista (Spixomyia) flaviventris sp. nov. (A) Epandrium, cerci and surstylus in lateral view; (B) same in dorsal view (setae omitted on entire portion); (C) hypandrium, pregonite, postgonite and aedeagus in lateral view; (D) abdominal fifth sternum in dorsal view (setae omitted on left side). Scale bars 0.2 mm." ;
        fabio:hasRepresentation  "https://zenodo.org/record/4594129/files/figure.png" .

